dct_title_s: Africa : mines and projects / compiled and produced by Intierra Mapping.
dct_description_sm: "August 2012." Relief shown by shading. Includes inset of Pretoria area locating mines and mining companies, text, and advertisements. Map of Africa, showing operating and closed mine locations and deposits. Panel title. At foot of title: August 2012.
